column1: Note:  "CPI" indicates IMF Consumer Price Index database.  "National sources" incldues the data from central banks, statitiscal offices, or other country-specific institutions. Base dates for CPI database are not avaialble for some countries.  For those countries where energy consumer price index (or its estiamte) is not available, consumer price index for the sector on housing, fuel, water, electricity, gas and other fuels  (COICOP 04) is used as proxy for energy prices.
